We run each simulation in three stages. The first stage yields equilibrium cell shapes, starting from a uniform square grid initial configuration. The duration of this step is 2900 MCS, and the motile force is switched off \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
